name: Fish Chunks
description: Fish Chunks are added to the Prospector's inventory after looting the carcass of a fish. Fish caught using a Fishing Trap or Fishing Rod can be converted into Fish Chunks as well. Fish Chunks can be cooked in a Campfire , or used in other dishes such as Freshwater Fillet Curry or Crumbed Saltwater Fillet . Right-click a Freshwater/Saltwater fish to convert it into Fish Chunks .
